        "content": "<p>Do we have anything like the following?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">theorem</span> <span class=\"n\">hasSum_telescope</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">TopologicalSpace</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">AddCommGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">TopologicalAddGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñï</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hx</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Tendsto</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">atTop</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">ùìù</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">HasSum</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñï</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
