        "timestamp": 1713260638
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Oh, Eric is only asking for the <em>sequence</em> to converge to zero, not for the <em>series</em> to be summable (though not necessarily absolutely)!</p>\n<p>Still, I am a little skeptical about S√©bastien's example.</p>",
